---
---

<section id="guide" class="py-[var(--spacing-section)]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <!-- Centered empathy statement -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20" data-animate="settle">
      <p class="font-mono text-smoke-gray uppercase mb-6" style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xs); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);">
        Your Guide
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-titanium-white italic" style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-3xl); line-height: var(--leading-snug);">
        We understand what is at stake.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Two-column authority grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24">
      <div data-animate="fade" data-animate-delay="1">
        <p class="font-mono text-smoke-gray uppercase mb-4" style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xs); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);">
          Empathy
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-shadow-gray" style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);">
          Commissioning a mural or restoring a sign is a significant investment. You need to know that the finished work will belong to your specific place in a way that cannot be replicated anywhere else.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-shadow-gray mt-6" style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-base); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);">
          We have watched property owners spend real money on work that looks beautiful in a portfolio but feels wrong on their wall. We built our process to solve that problem.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div data-animate="fade" data-animate-delay="2">
        <p class="font-mono text-smoke-gray uppercase mb-4" style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xs); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);">
          Authority
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-shadow-gray" style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);">
          Untitled Mixed Media has delivered murals and sign work for commercial buildings, historic properties, and public spaces across Richmond.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-shadow-gray mt-6" style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-base); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);">
          Our methodology is documented. Our results are permanent. Every project comes with a Certificate of Provenance tracing each design decision to its origin.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
